                <p>We present history with scholarly rigor and cultural sensitivity, partnering with museums to ensure accuracy.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-item">
                <div class="value-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                </div>
                <h4>Accessibility</h4>
                <p>Culture belongs to everyone. We break down barriers to make heritage universally accessible.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-item">
                <div class="value-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                </div>
                <h4>Innovation</h4>
                <p>We leverage cutting-edge technology to create experiences that honor the past while embracing the future.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="value-item">
                <div class="value-icon">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
